## Venn diagrams
Overview of protein overlaps between replicates of the same sample

```{r venn diagrams}
for (i in Run_annotations$Sample) {
  venn_list <- PGs %>%
    filter(Sample == i) %>%
    split(.$Batch) %>%
    lapply(function(df) {
      df %>%
        select(`Group Description`) %>%
        pull()
    })

  # make the plot
  ggVennDiagram(venn_list) +
    theme_void() +
    ggtitle(paste(i, "protein identification overlap")) +
    ggplot2::scale_fill_gradient(low = "white", high = "red")

  # Save the plot
  ggsave(paste0(output_dir, i, "replication venn diagram.png"), width = 8, height = 5.5)
}
```

